MAGMA-seq Unified Mutation Tree Visualization

Overview

Interactive visualization of parent-child mutation relationships in antibody affinity maturation using Dr. Whitehead's authoritative reference sequences:

  • Datasets: Kirby et al. 2025 and Petersen et al. 2024
  • X-axis: Number of mutations from reference sequence (0 = reference position)
  • Y-axis: Binding affinity (KD in nM, log scale)
  • Points: Individual experimental sequences
  • Interactivity: Hover for sequence details
